import React from 'react'
import Reminder from './Reminder/index.js'
import { reminderBox } from './Reminder/styles.js'
// import COMPONENT from 'FILEPATH'

const App = () => (

  <reminderBox style={{ justifyContent: "center", height: "100vh", width: "100vw", backgroundColor: "red" }}>
    <Reminder style={{ alignItems: "center" }} title="test">
      Beep boop. Hi there, I'm your personal assistant :D
    </Reminder>
  </reminderBox>
)

export default App
